description: Try our easy to follow Devondale Veggie Slice recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Devondale Veggie Slice Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 60ml Devondale Full Cream Long Life Milk
1 pinch black pepper, to taste (to taste)
1 pinch pink salt ground, to taste

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180°C. Line a 20x20cm ceramic baking dish or non-stick cake tin with baking paper.
Place all ingredients, except tomatoes, in a large bowl and stir to combine evenly.
Pour mixture into prepared tin and stud with cherry tomato halves. Bake at 180°C for 50-60 minutes or until golden and set. Rest for 15 minutes before slicing.
